      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i've mostly just been drinking more water like you said. i feel like the shaking is getting a bit more noticeable tho. do u think i should try taking a double dose of my water or maybe some extra electrolytes to help flush it out? i just want to make sure the levels stay okay",
